23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
24
25 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 20, Chapter 76, Subchapter 1, is
26 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
27 20-76-120. Waiver to enhance nutrition in the Supplemental Nutrition
28 Assistance Program.
29 The Secretary of the Department of Human Services shall request a
30 waiver from the United States Department of Agriculture to exclude candy and
31 soft drinks from the definition of eligible foods under 7 C.F.R. ยง 271.2, as
32 it existed on January 1, 2025.
33 (1) If a waiver requested under this section is granted, the
34 secretary shall prohibit the purchase of candy and soft drinks with benefits
35 provided through the Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program.
36 (2) If the waiver requested under this section is not granted,
